  <header class="brand-page__hero">
    <span class="brand-page__eyebrow">About Vastrini.label</span>
    <h1>A story of new beginnings, confidence, and everyday elegance.</h1>
  </header>

  <div class="brand-page__body">
    <p class="brand-page__lead">Vastrini.label was born from a simple dream: a dream of starting over, rediscovering confidence, and creating something beautiful for women who deserve to feel special every single day.</p>

    <p>Behind the brand is the story of a woman who believed it is never too late to begin again. A mid-aged woman with a love for fashion, elegance, and timeless style decided to turn her passion into something meaningful, not just for herself, but for every woman who wants to feel confident, graceful, and seen.</p>

    <p>What started as a small idea slowly became Vastrini.label, a space where fashion is not just about trends, but about emotions, confidence, and self-expression. From elegant Indian wear and trendy western outfits to glamorous party wear, statement jewellery, and stylish handbags, every piece is chosen with love and intention.</p>

    <p>We carefully pick every collection to bring styles that feel beautiful, comfortable, and empowering. Whether it is dressing up for a celebration, a special occasion, or simply wanting to feel good about yourself, Vastrini.label is here to make every woman shine in her own unique way.</p>

    <p>Our inspiration comes from real women: their strength, their journeys, their confidence, and their beauty. We believe fashion should never feel complicated; it should make you feel radiant, fearless, and unapologetically yourself.</p>

    <p>At Vastrini.label, this is more than a brand. It is a story of new beginnings, confidence, passion, and the belief that every woman deserves to feel beautiful at every stage of life.</p>
  </div>

